Subject: Re: [VB] Euro Tails on U.S. Bus?

The way I do it is disconnect the wire that runs from the T/S switch to the master cylinder, and run
a wire directly to your brake lights. This bypasses the "no blinking when the brakes are on" feature
if the switch.

